Ruby/GtkHtml2
=================
Ruby/GtkHtml2 is a Ruby binding of GtkHtml2

Requirements
------------
   Ruby: http://www.ruby-lang.org/
   GTK+: http://www.gtk.org/
   libgtkhtml2: http://www.gnome.org/

Install
-------
   0. install ruby-1.6.x, GTK+, libgtkhtml2, Ruby/GLib2, Ruby/GTK2.
   1. ruby extconf.rb
   2. make
   3. su
   4. make install

Copying
